name: Beastmaster Strikeforce - Quattro Fuego
description: Quattro Fuego is an elite sniper marksman that holds many world records across the galaxy in distance shooting. He's not only able to shoot incredibly accurately from set or prone positions but also has the ability to shoot accurately on the move and in flight. He also switches off to a plasma burst rifle and is able to breathe fire for close range combat. He's typically the lead point man for recon missions for the team.
